rejectIfSystemRegistrar\n  into one checkClientIdNotReserved helper.\n\n- david #5: parse comma-separated authorizationGrantTypes into a typed\n  Set\u003cAuthorizationGrantType\u003e once, via a service helper\n  (getAuthorizationGrantTypesSet). Storage stays comma-separated for\n  this PR; a proper typed column is a separate cleanup.\n\n- david #6: restore name not-null=\"true\" in HBM and re-add the\n  alter-set-not-null line in V2_44_2. Override Dhis2OAuth2Client.getName()\n  to fall back to (truncated) clientId when the field is null/empty,\n  so Hibernate persists a non-null value AND the schema validator at\n  POST /api/schemas/oAuth2Client doesn't reject UI pre-validation that\n  omits name. Add getRawName() so defaulting / preservation logic can\n  still distinguish \"caller didn't supply\" from the fallback.\n\nOAuth2ClientAdminValidator deleted; logic merged into the service.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e\nSigned-off-by: Morten Svanaes \u003cmsvanaes@dhis2.org\u003e","author":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"msvanaes@dhis2.org"},"id":"24dda3c879c0ea31373b4c6e2b4a57bc74388535","tree_id":"5f1fdcc14fcad34e60b6beb27bb1bd1823eead6b","timestamp":"2026-04-22T07:22:49Z","committer":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"msvanaes@dhis2.org"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/5591308","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.githu